messages.messageBody:
I've just uploaded a new article, 'The Japanese in Ayudhya in the
first half of the 17th century' to the Samurai Archives:

http://www.samurai-archives.com/jia.html

written by Cepo from the list here, it is a study of the Japanese in
Siam in the early 17th century.
